abstract: Andrew Ross Sorkin DealBook column recommends Pres-elect Trump seek advice on job creation from Elon Musk, owner of electric car firm Tesla, solar power provider SolarCity and rocket maker SpaceX; notes in last decade Musk created nearly 35,000 jobs, most of them in manufacturing, and that his corporation's technological advances spurred innovation and growth in auto and energy industries.
